    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "There is set forth the following unverified information relating to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the captioned matter which was furnished to this Bureau by a confidential",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "source whose reliability is unknown and who has requested that his identity not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "be revealed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "I was flying from [unclear] to Parkersburg, W. Va. this",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "afternoon (September 25, 1949) and about four miles airline",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "southwest of Parkersburg, I suddenly noticed a bright yellow",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "object coming directly towards me. It came at me with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "such speed, added to my 100 m.p.h. forward speed that it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "startled me and had passed by in a matter of a couple of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "seconds, but it passed by about 100 feet under my ship and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "about 50 feet to my right, and because of the dark green",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "background of the forests below I was able to get a fairly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "clear outline of the object, and what I believe is a very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "accurate description.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Color - bright canary yellow",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Length - about 15 to 18 inches",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Diameter - about 4\" in the largest part",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
